---
title: Farro, Chicken Breast and Halloumi Salad with Fig Dressing, Veggies and Toasted Almonds
description: Packed with chicken, veggies and tasty grains, this salad is a refreshing complement to the satisfying squeak and salty, creamy taste of halloumi cheese. Add in a sweet and savoury fig dressing, and you're set to go with this simple and delicious Mediterranean-inspired dish!
